    <p class="crumbs"><a href="/">Home</a> / FAQ</p>
    <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="block">
  <div class="wrap">
    <details class="faq-item" open>
      <summary>What kinds of venues does Magna-Tech work with?</summary>
      <p>Movie theaters and drive-ins, museums and planetariums, schools and universities, houses of worship, government and military facilities, cruise ships, shopping centers, and performing arts venues. See <a href="/solutions/">Solutions by Venue</a> for the full list.</p>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Do you sell equipment, or only design and install it?</summary>
      <p>Both. Our catalog at <a href="https://www.mteworld.com">mteworld.com</a> lists over 9,000 items, and we also design, install, and support the systems we sell. See <a href="/products/">Products</a>.</p>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Can I rent equipment instead of buying it?</summary>
      <p>Yes. We maintain an inventory of digital and film cinema equipment for short- and medium-term rental — useful for festivals, events, and temporary installations. See <a href="/services/rental-services/">Rental Services</a>.</p>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Do you ship internationally?</summary>
      <p>Yes, we ship worldwide and have offices and agents across the Americas, Europe, the Middle East, and Asia. See <a href="/partnership/our-offices-and-agents/">Offices &amp; Agents</a>.</p>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Is there a minimum order?</summary>
      <p>Yes, our minimum order is $100. Full terms are on our <a href="/about/terms-and-conditions-of-sale/">Terms and Conditions of Sale</a> page.</p>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Do you sell vintage or legacy cinema equipment?</summary>
      <p>Yes — through our eBay store and on our <a href="/vintage-equipment/">Vintage &amp; Legacy Equipment</a> page. We also restore analog equipment for props, museums, and personal collections.</p>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>How do I become a Magna-Tech partner or agent?</summary>
      <p>Visit <a href="/partnership/">Become a Partner</a> and tell us about your market and business. We work with distributors and agents worldwide.</p>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>How long has Magna-Tech been in business?</summary>
      <p>Since {{ company.founded }}, founded in New York City. Steven H. Krams has owned and led the company since 1995. See <a href="/about/about-mte/">About MTE</a>.</p>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>How do I get a quote or reach the right regional office?</summary>
      <p>Use the form on our <a href="/contact/">Contact page</a> — pick your region and we'll route your message to the right office.</p>
    </details>
  </div>
</section>

